# Installation

<%= partial 'download-button' %>

1. Download the dmg installer file containing the app
1. Open your 'Downloads' folder in Finder
1. Double click the installer to start it
1. Drag the Seshy icon into your 'Applications' folder
1. Double click the 'Applications' folder to open it
1. In the 'Applications' folder window double click the Seshy icon

## Are you new to Seshy?

If so, you may want to take a minute to read a quick description of [how it works](/how-it-works/).

